Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.56,0:02:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}黄昏村落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.50,0:02:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.30,0:02:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看这个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.40,0:02:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很过分吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.20,0:02:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生啊 男生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.80,0:02:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃木那家伙硬扯来着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.20,0:02:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.00,0:03:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 而且铃木那个家伙边笑边跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.50,0:03:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅 对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.40,0:03:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住他让他道歉的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.60,0:03:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道歉也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 已经坏了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.90,0:03:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 让他下地狱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这主意好 就这么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.60,0:03:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让地狱少女把铃木送下地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙那么讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如消失了好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.40,0:03:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你吓死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.70,0:04:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.00,0:04:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医院打电话给我的时候 我心跳都停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.30,0:04:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.20,0:04:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个好人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.70,0:04:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个司机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.50,0:04:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我不好他还一直道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.00,0:04:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 如果我在刚才的事故里死了的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.90,0:04:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一会恨那个司机吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.70,0:04:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个好人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.70,0:04:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果我死了你也想会杀死他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.70,0:04:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.10,0:04:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我越来越糊涂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.90,0:05:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.10,0:05:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定放弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.50,0:05:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.80,0:05:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会再在你面前提了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.90,0:05:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就都忘掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 把眼泪擦擦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.40,0:05:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.90,0:05:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 对方的日程安排如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.20,0:05:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.80,0:05:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,469)}妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.10,0:05:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样结束真的好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.30,0:05:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.00,0:05:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 好消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.80,0:05:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去夏威夷采访
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.50,0:05:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏威夷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.20,0:06:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以混在采访费用里 一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.10,0:06:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很简单的采访 就当去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享受大海吧 鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.50,0:06:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 不喜欢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.80,0:06:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是夏威夷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.70,0:06:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.60,0:06:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这下就决定了 马上就订票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.10,0:06:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去倒茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.50,0:06:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.50,0:06:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明把那个骗人的旅行社的电话记下了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.50,0:06:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.80,0:06:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识仙太郎吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.70,0:06:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.80,0:06:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.80,0:06:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.40,0:06:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧 请你住手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.20,0:07:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再妨碍你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.20,0:07:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会再追着你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.10,0:07:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以快离开我的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.90,0:07:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 不要接近她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.80,0:07:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 你意识恢复了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.20,0:07:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.20,0:07:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去就没有终结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.50,0:07:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢 她想告诉我什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须去见地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.20,0:07:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.00,0:07:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.50,0:07:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想知道答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.60,0:07:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.40,0:07:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么烦恼吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.20,0:08:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.40,0:08:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六道乡吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.20,0:08:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女和那个男孩曾在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.80,0:08:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和地狱少女又是什么关系呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.60,0:08:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要让你知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.80,0:08:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.90,0:08:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.20,0:09:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吓我啊 混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.00,0:09:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个季节 几乎就没有客人来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.30,0:09:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就冷 下雪的话又看不到难得的风景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.50,0:09:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年这个时候都是下雪天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人您运气真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.10,0:09:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.20,0:09:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.00,0:09:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢 真讨厌 才刚说就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经可以洗澡了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.30,0:09:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 去洗个澡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.00,0:09:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 说了奇怪的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来带路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.60,0:10:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候怎么办好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.10,0:10:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这风景中你感觉到什么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.00,0:10:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了 鸫 爸爸来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.00,0:11:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.00,0:11:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你对风景感觉到什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.50,0:11:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么偏僻的地方可是头一次来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 真是个好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.40,0:11:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.60,0:11:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天晴了真好 雪也没有积得恨深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.20,0:11:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想去什么地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.90,0:11:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这个村子里有个地方适合远眺风景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.00,0:12:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘 这个地方远吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.90,0:12:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里过去大概二十分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.20,0:12:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 请告诉我们怎么去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.40,0:12:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 现在可是冬天啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近的事情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.20,0:12:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我不是这里出生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.30,0:12:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去寺院问问怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.60,0:12:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.70,0:12:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好在去瀑布的途中有一座
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.30,0:12:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的住持可能会知道些吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.50,0:13:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽是粗茶 但亦能暖身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.80,0:13:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从东京来还真是远啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.60,0:13:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是这种季节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.10,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杂志的采访也真是很辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.70,0:13:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.60,0:13:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柴田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.70,0:13:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又是巧合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.20,0:13:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于从前的事情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.70,0:14:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也不是这里出身的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被请到这里来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.10,0:14:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.90,0:14:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我帮不上你的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.00,0:14:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.00,0:14:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是黑糖 很好吃的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.40,0:14:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑糖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.60,0:14:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持了以前的风味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.40,0:14:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.00,0:14:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.90,0:14:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我想起了一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.80,0:14:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“送七”的风俗不知你们可曾知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.50,0:14:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送七
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.40,0:14:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是以前这附近的风俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.00,0:14:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了向山神祈祷无病消灾五谷丰登
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.90,0:15:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每七年向山奉上刚满七岁的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.60,0:15:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把七岁的孩子献给山神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.50,0:15:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一样年纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.20,0:15:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七是代表阴阳中阳的数字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.50,0:15:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很吉祥的数字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被认为能象征喜事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.20,0:15:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并能带来喜事的数字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.30,0:15:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了给村子代来喜事就将七岁的孩子献给神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.00,0:16:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个寺就是为镇慰那些在山里徘徊的幼小的灵魂而建造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.20,0:16:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以名字就叫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.60,0:16:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 而且建这所寺庙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.80,0:16:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实就是做这黑糖的第一代当家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.40,0:16:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴建于四百年前安土桃山时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.00,0:16:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当家的本就是这里出身的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.90,0:16:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出于一些原因离开了这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.40,0:16:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来经营黑糖的店铺而成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.80,0:17:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在呢 似乎和第一代当家有血缘的人已经不在店里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.30,0:17:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是每年几次把糖当作供品送来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.00,0:17:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫什么的店呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.40,0:17:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 那就是我刚才说的巧合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.70,0:17:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫柴田屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柴田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.60,0:17:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.20,0:17:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.50,0:17:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住持 柴田家第一代的名字叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说叫仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.90,0:18:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子你那边似乎也没找到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.20,0:18:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们真是没用透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.50,0:18:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.80,0:18:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 小姐到哪儿去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.20,0:18:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是去做事最近一不留神就不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.70,0:18:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 小姐也差不多到这年纪了 好疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是开玩笑的时候嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.00,0:18:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不用丢我吧 好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.10,0:18:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.00,0:18:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.10,0:18:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.00,0:18:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 难不成…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.80,0:19:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到的风景是这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.70,0:19:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁堆的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.10,0:19:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.10,0:19:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.20,0:19:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.70,0:19:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 放开我仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.50,0:19:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.10,0:19:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.80,0:19:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女和仙太郎两个人是青梅竹马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.10,0:20:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.50,0:20:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还留着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.30,0:20:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今不祥之血还没有断绝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.70,0:20:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那血使我迷乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.60,0:20:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不祥 你到底在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.00,0:20:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧 住手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 住手吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.60,0:20:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.60,0:20:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧 仙太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.80,0:20:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸫 没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被活埋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.20,0:20:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被活埋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.80,0:21:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被仙太郎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.50,0:21:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想杀我一次吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.10,0:21:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越了时间的你又想像那时一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.90,0:21:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经承担了一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.60,0:21:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再被杀死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.90,0:21:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.90,0:21:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.40,0:21:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.10,0:21:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 不能凭感情杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.00,0:21:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐会被送下地狱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.20,0:21:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那样也无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.20,0:21:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 心灵被憎恨支配了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.70,0:22:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.50,0:22:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么 快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.90,0:22:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.50,0:22:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.80,0:22:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.40,0:22:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.90,0:22:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.70,0:22:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨 流向地狱就好
